freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had a fever Feb 25 during the evening and night 100.7. Chills. Fine until the Evening of the 26th when I had the same symptoms. Fine since then.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: My arm is little more  sore At the site today than previous days.
My face was red 1 hour after the vaccine. No other allergy symptoms
The injection site is more tender today
These symptoms were present until 5am 2/20/21. I received my vaccine 6:15pm 2/18:21
